's AIs Push Directly\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies — Do NOT default to a feature-branch + PR flow, do NOT re-ask whether to use a PR, and do NOT flag the bypass or the unsi… | Prioritize when: only (the tree often has concurrent parallel-session work + daemon metadata churn — NEVER `git add -A` blindly; use exp…\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"triggered\": [\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 6626,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/001-fix-command-dispatch/z_archive/007-system-spec-kit-rename\",\n          \"title\": \"Skill Rename [system-spec-kit/z_archive/001-fix-command-dispatch/z_archive/007-system-spec-kit-rename/spec]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"skill\",\n            \"workflows\",\n            \"spec\",\n            \"kit\",\n            \"system\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 7589,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/022-hybrid-rag-fusion/005-architecture-audit\",\n          \"title\": \"System-Spec-Kit Architecture Audit v2 [system-spec-kit/022-hybrid-rag-fusion/005-architecture-audit/research]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"system\",\n            \"spec\",\n            \"kit\",\n            \"research\",\n            \"005\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 7426,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/021-spec-kit-phase-system\",\n          \"title\": \"Verification Checklist: SpecKit Phase System [system-spec-kit/021-spec-kit-phase-system/checklist]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"verification\",\n            \"phase\",\n            \"system\",\n            \"021\",\n            \"spec\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 6623,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/001-fix-command-dispatch/z_archive/007-system-spec-kit-rename\",\n          \"title\": \"Verification [system-spec-kit/z_archive/001-fix-command-dispatch/z_archive/007-system-spec-kit-rename/checklist]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"verification\",\n            \"workflows\",\n            \"spec\",\n            \"kit\",\n            \"system\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 7434,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/021-spec-kit-phase-system\",\n          \"title\": \"Feature Specification: SpecKit Phase System [system-spec-kit/021-spec-kit-phase-system/spec]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"phase\",\n            \"system\",\n            \"spec\",\n            \"021\"\n          ]\n        }\n      ],\n      \"surfaced_at\": \"2026-06-18T06:00:37.643Z\",\n      \"latencyMs\": 37\n    },\n    \"tokenBudget\": 3500\n  }\n}","metadata":{"truncated":false},"title":"","time":{"start":1781762437599,"end":1781762437665}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0a9c1fa9f62e3ffa016a338983700c8191b5c822c722a79dcf"}},"id":"prt_ed95129ca001sxpKPPMiaKqVDe","sessionID":"ses_126af6eadffeKdnQM4mriL3y8K","messageID":"msg_ed95115e7001eUnWOHzOtCoz9b"}}
